(12, 0, '1', 'AVS Address Mismatch EG0033882: Brian Earley', 'Member is Inactive and when I try to process past dues, it declines and says address mismatch. Member is a training client and his address has not changed from 2200 Dalewood Ct. Plainfield IL 60586. Please advise. (not the only time I have seen this happen either). Thank you.', 3, 9, '1441911463', '', '2015-09-10 13:27:43'),
