(14, 0, '1', 'Geoffrey Hoyles EG0023303', 'I spoke with Geoffrey Hoyles.  His agreement end date was this month.  He was never told his membership would go month-to-month after his agreement ended.  He is not renewing his membership.  Please stop further billing.', 3, 8, '1441916871', '', '2015-09-10 14:57:51'),
(15, 0, '1', 'Freeze Inactive to Freeze Active', 'EG0033790 :GaryPaisley. Please make sure member is in Freeze Active Status. Thank you.', 3, 9, '1441923074', '', '2015-09-10 16:41:14'),
(16, 0, '1', 'Fernando Pulido EG0015216 - Naperville', 'Fernando Pulido EG0015216 - Naperville\nFlex Member\n0 workouts - Paid $0.00\nFree Month? - Advise as to why', 3, 2, '1441989049', '', '2015-09-11 11:00:49'),
(17, 0, '1', 'Scott Allgood EG0015054 - Naperville - Data Consistency Issue', 'Scott Allgood EG0015054 - Naperville\nActive in Eco Gym\nInactive in Eco Impressions', 3, 2, '1441989087', '', '2015-09-11 11:01:27'),
(18, 0, '1', 'Work Out Log between Clubs', 'Many customers are working out between Naperville and Plainfield:\nMember signed up in Naperville with an EG001***\nPhil registers the fingerprint in Plainfield in Eco Impression with their original member number\nAlso registered in BioManager in Naperville\nWe switched to Eco Impression in Naperville\nCustomer who is an EG001** ID, can''t access Naperville even though they have access in Plainfield\nExample Max Bednarski - EG0011514\nWhen trying to enter fingerprint in Eco Impression (Naperville), says "member number already exists"\nThis issue also happens with Plainfield members trying to use Naperville''s club.\nHow do we fix this and when will Global access work?', 1, 2, '1441989129', '', '2015-09-11 11:02:09'),
(19, 1, '1', 'Evan Marinis EG0025308', 'Evan Marinis EG0025308 is in a "no join" status. Problem is, I found a 2 month agreement for him that was signed on 6/29/15. The total payment was supposed to be a one time $99 charge.The way I am understanding this is, we never processed any payment for him. Should I just go ahead and process it? Also, how do I make sure that it does not get set as a recurring payment?', 1, 8, '1441990029', '', '2015-09-11 11:17:09'),
(20, 0, '1', 'Evan Marinis EG0025308', 'I spoke with chris gellings on the phone about this so nevermind my question earlier. Please process a 2 month membership from 6/29/15 totaling $99 with no recurring payments. It will go on a Visa card. CC# 4388-5266-7543-7619 expiring 06/2016.', 3, 8, '1441993556', '', '2015-09-11 12:15:56'),
(21, 0, '1', 'Jeff Young EG0015267', 'Please cancel with 30 day notice.  Member moved and brought in proper documents.  Documents on file at gym. Do not charge cancel fee.', 3, 7, '1442002739', '', '2015-09-11 14:48:59'),
(22, 0, '1', 'Danny David EG0025083', 'this is a duplicate "no join" account for an active member. please remove from report', 3, 8, '1442003207', '', '2015-09-11 14:56:47'),
(23, 0, '1', 'Julie Ford EG0022635', 'Matt Newman spoke with Julie Ford. She is supposed to be a complementary member because she is a personal training client. Please make our records reflect this. Matt can be reached at mnewman@ecogymworldwide.com with any further questions regarding this.', 3, 8, '1442003795', '', '2015-09-11 15:06:35'),
(24, 0, '1', 'Jeff Amport EG0015548', 'Please refund $59 dollars to credit card on file.  Member switched from Plainfield to Naperville and works out more than 26 times a month.', 3, 7, '1442004310', '', '2015-09-11 15:15:10'),
