(29, 0, '1', 'College Member Cancellation EG0034771', 'Nicholas Carter EG0034771 was only supposed to be a Flex member for 5 months due to college in August and leaving early for the baseball team. We unfortunately did not have any seasonal four month memberships at this time. \nPrevious Fitness Counselor set up the membership and did not notify me or adjust the end to August 13th. Please cancel immediately and do not charge $200 cancel fee. I have spoken with is father Charles, who was financially the one responsible for the account with us. Member will be returning next Summer and enrolling in our seasonal option. Thank you.', 3, 9, '1442255805', '', '2015-09-14 13:06:45'),
