(38, 0, '1', 'deactivated fingerprints', 'this morning so far, I have run into 2 members who could not scan in. Mike''s (employee) prints were deactivated along with mine for some reason. I have no way of knowing who else this happened to. What should I do about this?', 3, 8, '1442328648', '', '2015-09-15 09:20:48'),
