(226, 0, '1', 'Billing', '<p>This is from Phil - I approve.</p><p>Michael,</p><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Member ID # EG0033966 Victoria Brewton activated on 1/26/15 as a fixed rate m2m member. She was given a 14 day SG from our discount center. Her husband had spoken with Justin Barton in January regarding her not continuing with us. She was refunded four $49 amounts, but I miscommunicated to Vaazu team and she should have had two additional $49 returned back to her. Can you please issue her account a $98 refund for bill dates 2/26/ and 3/26.</div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Also, the husband Preston Brewton EG0033965 was billed $19.97 x 2 in August and September and should have not been, due to him being cancelled with 30 days notice on file. He will be joining the club after the first of the year with us as he is moving his business back to Plainfield. I have already put the cancel request in and he will cancel on 10/25/15. Please return the $39.94 to this member as well. </div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">I will make up this $137.94 by the end of the month easily. I met this gentleman through the Chamber and do not want a bad taste in his mouth. I am trying to pay it forward in a sense. Thank you. </div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></div><div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please use COF 3975. <br/><div><div dir="ltr"><div><div dir="ltr"><div><br/></div><div>Yours in Eco-Friendly Health,</div></div></div></div></div></div>', 5, 2, '1444861093', '', '2015-10-14 16:48:13'),
