(236, 0, '1', 'Ron  Losoya EG0025646', '<p>I am trying to set this member up on a month to month $49 fixed rate with a mini membership and waive his start up fee of $79. this option is not available in my drop down menu to select. please make sure that he does not pay the $79 biometric/security fee. his total down payment should be $98. thank you</p>', 3, 8, '1444953917', '', '2015-10-15 18:35:17'),
(237, 0, '1', 'EG0034771', '<p>Please cancel member ID EG0034771 (Nick Carter). He enrolled as a college member before we had the seasonal options available. He did fill out cancel form on September 12th. </p><p>Please cancel immediately and refund last dues taken totaling $78.97. Thank you. </p>', 3, 9, '1445015147', '', '2015-10-16 11:35:47'),
(238, 0, '3', 'Ron Losoya EG0025646', '<p>member is active in eco gym but I could not take his picture on eco impressions, therefore I am unable to register fingerprints</p>', 6, 8, '1445094092', '', '2015-10-17 09:31:32'),
(239, 0, '1', 'Marc Hunter EG0010945', '<p>Please cancel Marc Hunter EG0010945 as he is a Complimentary member cncelling. Please forgive past due balance from recent club enhancement fee of $29.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1445096526', '', '2015-10-17 10:12:06'),
(240, 0, '1', 'Marshall Gerber EG0021825', '<p>member is unable to log on to eco gym website. I have tried helping him log in, and from what I can tell, he is doing everything correctly. please advise</p>', 3, 8, '1445271551', '', '2015-10-19 10:49:11'),
(241, 0, '1', 'Leslie BrownEG0023076', '<p>please forgive the declined transaction of $29 club enhancement fee. this is my mother and she was told she would pay nothing to be a member here (she does not come anyways)</p>', 3, 8, '1445273733', '', '2015-10-19 11:25:33'),
(242, 0, '1', 'Mathew Pelos EG0025357', '<p>member was supposed to be canceled with no further billing. he just saw a club enhancement fee of $29 on his account. please explain</p>', 5, 8, '1445275950', '', '2015-10-19 12:02:30'),
(243, 1, '1', 'Daiva Evans EG0021615', '<p>is there a way to tell when this members cancel request was initially put in? I cannot tell on my end</p>', 0, 8, '1445279636', '', '2015-10-19 13:03:56'),
(244, 0, '1', 'EG0035045', '<p>Member enrolled M2M @ $19 with $90 of Group Training and $168=$297 on 4/29/15. Member was over charged on June 3rd ($30), which was premature for the reoccurring, which should have been 7/29/15 if the service was kept on the account. </p><p> Member wanted to cancel add on service due to over charge on June 3. System still charged 7/29 and 8/29 and 9/29 for some reason, when it had been removed. (data migration maybe??). Please refund only the last two $30 group training payments to customer for over charge on group training. member has been cancelled and will expire on 10/28/15. The $29 club enhancement stays with the club and is owed to us. 30 Days notice was given on 9/25/15. Thank you.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', 3, 9, '1445285394', '', '2015-10-19 14:39:54'),
(245, 0, '1', 'Beth Kohorn EG0011353', '<p>Please Refund Beth Kohorn EG0011353 ($60) to the card on file. She had cancelled in June and has been over-billed August and September.</p><p>Thank you.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1445289013', '', '2015-10-19 15:40:13'),
(246, 0, '1', 'EG0035393', '<p>Member enrolled M2M and came in on 9/8/15 to fill out cancel form on file. Last month''s dues should be 9/24/15 only. Please cancel immediately and remove decline $29 as member gave 30 days notice 9/8/15. I did not realize the club enhancement due was still set to come out automatically on 10/15/15 and did not inform member they would be charged this on the cancel form. My communication error to member. </p><p><br/></p><p> I did not put through cancellation on website, but will today for you guys. My apologies. Member needs to cancel on 10/23/15. Thank you. </p>', 3, 9, '1445289476', '', '2015-10-19 15:47:56'),
(247, 0, '1', 'EG0035469', '<p>Member enrolled as a cash $19.97 child add on (referral from local doctor we work with) Only paid for two months upfront ($39.94) 9/2/15-11/2/15. Member is not responsible for $29 club enhancement fee per my approval. </p><p><br/></p><p>I did not think to inform member on this 10/15 club enhancement fee at the time of sign up. Please remove decline fee as I do not have a CC on file to charge it and make join green active again. Also, please make sure member auto expires on 11/2/15. Thank you.</p>', 1, 9, '1445289767', '', '2015-10-19 15:52:47'),
(248, 0, '1', 'Kyle Rosales EG0014087', '<p>Please credit Kyle Rosales EG0014087, 7 workouts. October (11,12,13,14,16,18,and 19).  Thank you.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1445367016', '', '2015-10-20 13:20:16'),
(249, 0, '1', 'Jake Cuvala EG0014097', '<p>Please credit Jake Cuvala EG0014097 in the amount of $30 back to the card on file as biometric system inaccurately tracked his visits. </p><p><span>I am looking into the issue. EcoImpressions and Eco Gym indicates 3 visits between (9/20/15 - 10/19/15). His track-record indicates visiting between 19-28 times each month since joining. He is traditionally billed $0, $19, and $29. This past month was $49.</span><br/></p><p><span><br/></span></p><p><span>Thank you.</span></p><p><span><br/></span></p><p><span>-Chris</span></p>', 3, 10, '1445373348', '', '2015-10-20 15:05:48'),
(250, 0, '3', 'camera issue', '<p>again I am unable to take a picture of a member when I am trying to enroll them. because of this, I cannot save fingerprints. please advise</p>', 3, 8, '1445373485', '', '2015-10-20 15:08:05'),
(251, 0, '1', 'Elizabeth Nestos EG0025661', '<p>member started a 6month complementary membership today (gift certificate). Please make sure that this has an end date 6 months from now. thank you</p>', 3, 8, '1445376808', '', '2015-10-20 16:03:28'),
(252, 0, '1', 'Erica Conway EG0015248', '<p>Please credit Erica Conway EG0015248 $58 to the card on file, as a customer service decision, as she has had trouble logging workouts between new biometric systems in Naperville. (Sept and Oct)</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1445383324', '', '2015-10-20 17:52:04'),
(253, 0, '1', 'Hours of Operation', '<p>As the hours of operation are accurate for all locations (Glenview, Naperville, and Plainfield) on the website (11am - 7pm Mon -Thurs, Fri 11am - 5pm, Sat/Sun By Appointment Only. The hours of operation when someone registers online for 7-Day Free Trail Pass on Mobile is 6:30am - 8pm Mon-Fri, Sat 9:30am - 3pm (I believe) and Sun - By Appointment Only.</p><p><br/></p><p>Please make the necessary adjustments to the Trial Pass for both Mobile and Web applications for all clubs, (Glenview, Naperville, and Plainfield) (11am - 7pm Mon -Thurs, Fri 11am - 5pm, Sat/Sun By Appointment Only.</p><p>Thank you.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 5, 10, '1445392361', '', '2015-10-20 20:22:41'),
(254, 0, '1', 'EG0034605', '<p>Kelli Tufo EG0034605 was frozen on 7/17/15 for hip surgery for 30 days. She has decided to come back in and unfreeze her membership.</p><p><br/></p><p>Please activate her Flex membership on 10/21/15, do not bill anything as her next flex bill date will be 11/20/15 based on workouts from previous 30 days. Is this correct? Please advise. Thank you</p>', 3, 9, '1445392942', '', '2015-10-20 20:32:22'),
(255, 0, '1', 'EG0034844', '<p>Karen Espinoza signed her 17 year old daughter up under an 18 month membership. Mother wishes to cancel Flex program. Form filled on with signature on file. Last flex on 10/30/15 and the system for some reason said M2M option? She is on Flex and needs to be charged the early termination fee of $200 on 11/29/15 (effective cancellation date). Thank you. </p>', 3, 9, '1445393783', '', '2015-10-20 20:46:23'),
(256, 0, '1', 'EG0035227', '<p>Membe: <span style="color: black;">EG0035227 Jordyn Screeton</span></p><p>-was in car accident and has fractured foot. Will be on crutches for 2-4 weeks. She is on Flex. Please freeze from 11/8-12/8 and charge $15 for freeze fee. Please reactivate Flex on 12-8. Thank you</p>', 3, 9, '1445449666', '', '2015-10-21 12:17:46'),
(257, 0, '3', 'Julie Ford EG0022635', '<p>for some reason this member has had continuing issues with her prints getting deactivated. I have made sure that anything that is owed to us is paid and   she is in active status in eco gym. I have again reactivated her prints on my end. please make sure they stay active. </p>', 3, 8, '1445535134', '', '2015-10-22 12:02:14'),
(258, 0, '3', 'DJ Arrigo EG0024232', '<p>member is active. i have activated prints. please make sure they stay active</p>', 3, 8, '1445546699', '', '2015-10-22 15:14:59'),
(259, 0, '1', 'EG0035549', '<p>Please make sure member is not billed for $30 group training classes on 11/10/15. 30 days was given before member went out of town, but service was not removed with in 30 days advanced notice. Thank you </p>', 3, 9, '1445553870', '', '2015-10-22 17:14:30'),
(260, 0, '1', 'EG0035550', '<p>Please make sure member is not billed for $30 group training classes on 11/10/15. 30 days was given before member went out of town, but service was not removed with in 30 days advanced notice. <br/></p>', 3, 9, '1445553890', '', '2015-10-22 17:14:50'),
(261, 0, '1', 'EG0033955', '<p>Member is on Flex option and cancellation was put through on 10/23/15. Last Flex on 10/26/15 and $200 should be billed on 11/25/15, but system did not default to this function. Please charge $200 on 11/25/15 when membership cancels. Thank you. </p>', 3, 9, '1445624625', '', '2015-10-23 12:53:45'),
(262, 0, '1', 'Seema Bendre EG0022361', '<p>please ignore past due balance on account and cancel out member. member never intended to join the gym in the first place. I do now have a cancelation form on file though</p>', 3, 8, '1445626951', '', '2015-10-23 13:32:31'),
(263, 0, '1', 'EG0034903', '<p>Member was charge $29 on 10/20/15. I have their bank statement showing this charge. I do not see this $29 charge on member''s account history. Please advise and reverse/refund charge if it was not authorized by member. Thank you </p>', 3, 9, '1445628910', '', '2015-10-23 14:05:10'),
(264, 0, '3', 'EG0014512 Charlie Radeke', '<ul><li>EG0014512 Charlie Radeke.</li><li><span>Member needs 24 visits added to the current pay period (10/01 - 10/31, wherever dates are available). </span></li><li><span>The PIN that he was given by former Naperville staff (2690) is not connected to his account so his workouts were not being tracked. </span></li><li><span>The PIN 2690 is attached to member Tommy Hojinicki (member number ADD4?...). </span></li><li><span>Charlie originally signed up in the Naperville club but registered in EcoImpressions in Plainfield.</span><br/></li><li><span>Please enable Charlie to be tracked at both Naperville and Plainfield for his Flex visits.</span></li></ul><p><br/></p><p>Thank You.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Rob</p>', 3, 13, '1445631654', '', '2015-10-23 14:50:54'),
(265, 0, '2', 'Problem Reactivating Sessions on FMG', '<ul><li>When I go to unexpire a session with client Megan Milano (not paying trainer or charging client session) the site pops up a window and states that FMG is encountering a problem </li><li>This problem also happens with other clients with expired sessions </li></ul><p><br/></p><p>Thanks </p><p><br/></p><p>-Rob</p>', 5, 13, '1445891095', '', '2015-10-26 14:54:55'),
(266, 0, '3', 'EG0011362 Janet LoVerde', '<p>EG0011362 Janet LoVerde<br/></p><ul><li>PIN number can be entered on keypad once but when prompted to re-enter the PIN a second time it will not go through </li><li>PIN is recognized the first time it is entered </li></ul><p><br/></p><p>thanks </p><p><br/></p><p>-Sarah</p><p><br/></p>', 3, 12, '1445891695', '', '2015-10-26 15:04:55'),
(267, 0, '1', 'Charlie Radeke EG0014512', '<ul><li>Charlie Radeke EG0014512<br/></li><li>Member needs 24 visits added to current bill period 10/1-10/31</li><li>member previously had an incorrect pin associated to his account so his workouts for his flex membership did not track to him </li></ul><p><br/></p><p>thanks</p><p><br/></p><p>-rob</p>', 5, 13, '1445943580', '', '2015-10-27 05:29:40'),
(268, 0, '1', 'Faith Buishas EG0014385', '<p>Please add 1 workout on 10/23/15 for Faith Buishas EG0014385</p><p><br/></p><p>Thank you.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 6, 10, '1445971651', '', '2015-10-27 13:17:31'),
(269, 0, '3', 'Craig Brzezinski EG0015369', '<p>Please give Craig Brzezinski EG0015369 access to Naperville EcoIpmressions. </p><ul><li>He is a Naperville Member who joined Naperville. </li><li>Registered his prints in Plainfield</li><li>Member Number Already Exists</li><li>Cannot access the club in Naperville</li></ul><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1445971799', '', '2015-10-27 13:19:59'),
(270, 0, '3', 'Tyler Nichols EG0035006', '<p>Please give Tyler Nichols EG0035006 access to Naperville Club to register Flex workouts. He is a Plainfield Member.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1445971893', '', '2015-10-27 13:21:33'),
(271, 0, '1', 'EG0033677', '<p>Member joined during discount center for $1 on flex with husband. Member EG0033677 relocated to California back in May. I have proof of new lease agreement, husband still is a member and I have been working with Chris (husband) on closing wife''s account by charging some of the past due amounts on his card. </p><p><br/></p><p>Member EG0033677 is not responsible per my approval for remaining charges. Please cancel immediately and move to cancelled status. Member does not show any club usage at all. I do not want to charge this member further due to husband remaining a good standing member with us. Thank you</p><p><br/></p>', 3, 9, '1445984565', '', '2015-10-27 16:52:45'),
(272, 0, '1', 'EG0034342', '<p>Member EG0034342 was paying for a child add on under hyperbaric therapy due to the system not having a child add on option at the same cost as $19.97 for hyperbaric, we have now activated the son (child add on) for his own $19.97 monthly fee.</p><p><br/></p><p> Please remove $19.97 decline and return member EG0034342 to join active green status for club entry purposes on weekends. thank you</p>', 3, 9, '1445985493', '', '2015-10-27 17:08:13'),
(273, 0, '1', 'David Lee Josupait EG0015588', '<p>Please cancel David Lee Josupait EG0015588 WITHOUT $200 and refund the last $49 and $29 fee back to the card on file. Membership was a 14-Day cancellation and was not processed successfully by staff.  Thank you.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p><p><br/></p>', 3, 10, '1445988759', '', '2015-10-27 18:02:39'),
(274, 0, '1', 'Roberto Gutierrez EG0015589', '<p>Please refund Roberto Gutierrez EG0015589 $59 back to the card on file as he was a 14-day cancellation.  Thank you.</p><p>-Chris</p>', 6, 10, '1445988836', '', '2015-10-27 18:03:56'),
(275, 0, '1', 'EG0034840', '<p>Member EG0034840 joined using ex-boyfriends Credit Card ending 8978. Please refund the last $59 payment as he was threatening to call the police on Rose (EG0034840), who is still a member with us. </p><p><br/></p><p>She would like to be charged that $59 on card ending 0259. I saw a decline and charged the wrong card on file. Card ending 8978 has been deleted. Thank you. I can re run the charge on the card ending 0259 if I need to. </p>', 3, 9, '1445989044', '', '2015-10-27 18:07:24'),
(276, 0, '1', 'Drew Kulikowski EG0011022', '<p>Please charge Drew Kulikowski EG0011022 an early termination fee of $200.00 as he is canceling today.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1446049936', '', '2015-10-28 11:02:16'),
(277, 0, '1', 'Guiliana Bryza EG0035583', '<p>Can you please make Guiliana Bryza EG0035583 a complimentary member in Plainfield, IL?</p><p>Thanks,</p><p>Maggie</p>', 6, 2, '1446050885', '', '2015-10-28 11:18:05'),
(278, 0, '1', 'Jimmy Zebold EG0035584', '<p><title></title></p><p class="p1">Can you please make Jimmy Zebold EG0035584 a complimentary member in Plainfield, IL?</p><p class="p1">Thanks,</p><p class="p1">Maggie</p>', 6, 2, '1446050966', '', '2015-10-28 11:19:26'),
(279, 0, '3', 'Persons using both Naperville and Plainfield', '<p><title></title></p><p class="p1">The below customers are both using Naperville and Plainfield.</p><p class="p1">Can you please add their prints to both directories?</p><p class="p1">Bianca Rivera EG0034922</p><p class="p1">Teague Sullivan EG0035457</p><p class="p1">Thanks,</p><p class="p1">Maggie</p>', 6, 2, '1446051063', '', '2015-10-28 11:21:03'),
(280, 0, '3', 'Client using both Naperville and Plainfield - added to both directories', '<p><title></title></p><p class="p1">Below client is using both Naperville and Plainfield. Can you please enter their prints to both Naperville and Plainfield directories?</p><p class="p1">Ivan Sarabia EG0034230</p><p class="p1"><br/></p><p class="p1">Thanks,</p><p class="p1">Maggie</p>', 6, 2, '1446051144', '', '2015-10-28 11:22:24'),
(281, 0, '1', 'EG0034903 Email sent to Deepika/Michael/Chris on 10/28/15', '<div class="col-sm-12 clearfix ng-binding" style="float: left;width: 1219.44px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">EG0034903</div><div class="col-sm-12" style="float: left;width: 1219.44px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><div class="desc ng-binding"><p>Member was charge $29 on 10/20/15. I have their bank statement showing this charge (see email sent to Deepika). I do not see this $29 charge on member''s account history. Please advise and reverse/refund charge if it was not authorized by member. Thank you </p></div></div>', 3, 9, '1446056502', '', '2015-10-28 12:51:42'),
(282, 0, '1', 'Andrew Fox EG0015480', '<p>Please refund Andrew Fox EG0015480 $118.97 to the card ending in 5004. He cancelled the card ending in 8876 prior to canceling and never received the 14-day refund.  Thank you.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 3, 10, '1446065460', '', '2015-10-28 15:21:00'),
(283, 0, '1', 'Armand Barard EG0024761', '<p>Member is canceling due to relocation back to South Africa. I have processed his cancelation but please make sure that the $200 early termination fee is not applied. I could not remove the charge on my end</p>', 3, 8, '1446135375', '', '2015-10-29 10:46:15'),
(284, 0, '1', 'Ron Losoya EG0025646', '<p><title></title></p><p class="p1">Can you please refund Ron Losoya EG0025646, $79.</p><p class="p1">His recurring payments are the $49 fixed rate month to month will continue as normal.</p><p class="p1">we do not need to cancel account, just refund $79.</p><p class="p1">Thanks,</p><p class="p1">Maggie</p>', 6, 2, '1446135796', '', '2015-10-29 10:53:16'),
(285, 0, '1', 'Brady Nagel EG0025152', '<p>This member was on a college membership over the summer that should not have been set up on a recurring payment of $200 but it was. they saw charges of $200 and $29 in October. a refund needs to be issued for $229 please. </p>', 3, 8, '1446138171', '', '2015-10-29 11:32:51'),
(286, 0, '1', 'EG0035042', '<p>Member was given M2M option on Flex due to a planned pregnancy at the time of sign up. Philip gave the permission on this. Please remove early termination fee of $200. I have already put cancel request through website, but it defaults as it should to a $200 termination fee. Member paid $59 up front already for last month starting 11/28-12/27. Thank you. </p>', 3, 9, '1446143693', '', '2015-10-29 13:04:53'),
(287, 0, '3', 'Shelly Cinnamon EG0035496', '<p>Please grant Shelly Cinnamon EG0035496 (Plainfield Member) access to EcoImpressions in Naperville to use the Naperville Club.</p><p><br/></p><p>-Chris</p>', 6, 10, '1446153306', '', '2015-10-29 15:45:06'),
(288, 0, '1', 'EG0034948', '<p>Cancel form on file with proof of relocation (new lease agreement) to chicago. I have put through cancellation request on website, please remove $200 cancellation fee. Thank you. </p>', 3, 9, '1446223586', '', '2015-10-30 11:16:26'),
(289, 0, '1', 'Adam Pinto EG0025693', '<p>Please make the start date of this members recurring $20 hyperbaric payment start on 1/30/16. I did not change the start date when I processed his membership by mistake. sorry</p>', 3, 8, '1446229516', '', '2015-10-30 12:55:16'),
